---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Physical AI Workshop">
  <div class="workshop-container">
    <div class="hero-info">
      <h1>Physical AI Workshop</h1>
      <div class="event-details">
        <p class="date">🗓️ 2025년 8월 14일 (목) 14:00-18:00</p>
        <p class="location">📍 로보티즈 사옥 + 유튜브 라이브</p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSff0Sh3kSIl31J6mj4DX-Q5n5DCl9LYnqH3ZsTN3K8gydznXA/viewform?usp=sharing&ouid=109247284085622604521" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="register-btn">
        참가 신청하기
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="poster-section">
      <img src="/community/events/2025/physical-ai-workshop-poster.png" alt="Physical AI Workshop Poster" class="poster" />
    </div>

    <section class="event-info">
      <h2>행사 소개</h2>
      <p>Physical AI 시대를 준비하는 로봇 산업과 AI 기술의 융합에 대한 논의</p>
      <p>로봇 회사, 스타트업, 연구기관의 전문가들이 모여 Physical AI의 현재와 미래를 논의하는 워크숍입니다.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="speakers">
      <h2>발표자 소개</h2>
      <div class="speakers-grid">
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>로봇 회사가 준비하는<br/>Physical AI 시대</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">표윤석 이사</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">로보티즈 이사<br/>ROS 개발 경험 및 저서 출간<br/>큐슈대학교 정보지능공학 박사</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>VLA, Physical AI를<br/>구현하기 위한 AI</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">조준호 박사</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">삼성전자 Research Engineer<br/>서울대학교 전기정보공학부 박사</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>로봇 스타트업에서<br/>바라보는 Physical AI</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">하영열 대표</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">SEENGRIP 대표<br/>前 삼성중공업 엔지니어<br/>산업계측제어기술사</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="speaker-card">
          <h3>Physical AI 시대를<br/>준비하는 논의 (Q&A)</h3>
          <p class="speaker-name">박종현 대표</p>
          <p class="speaker-info">수도리무브 대표<br/>MS, 현대차 등과 AI로봇 프로젝트 수행<br/>삼성/SK 외 기관에서 AI 컨설팅 수행</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hands-on">
      <h2>특별 전시</h2>
      <div class="video-grid">
        <div class="video-card">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WNpRlIr4zbw"
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
          <p>로보티즈 제품 소개</p>
        </div>
        <div class="video-card">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3x-eN36pNns"
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
          <p>Physical AI 기술 시연</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="registration">
      <h2>참가 신청</h2>
      <p>Physical AI의 미래를 함께 만들어갈 분들의 많은 참여 부탁드립니다.</p>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSff0Sh3kSIl31J6mj4DX-Q5n5DCl9LYnqH3ZsTN3K8gydznXA/viewform?usp=sharing&ouid=109247284085622604521" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="register-btn-large">
        참가 신청 바로가기
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="host-info">
      <h2>주최</h2>
      <p><strong>SUDOREMOVE</strong> · <strong>SK마이써니</strong> · <strong>ROBOTIS</strong></p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --primary-color: #1a0f1f;
    --secondary-color: #251730;
    --accent-color: #fd7318;
    --text-color: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: #b8b8b8;
    --color-green: #43d6a8;
    --color-blue: #5fadfe;
  }

  body {
    background: #0d030f !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  .workshop-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .hero-info {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero-info h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-green);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .poster-section {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .poster {
    max-width: 500px;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .event-details {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .event-details p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .register-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .register-btn:hover {
    background: #e55f0a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.4);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .event-info p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .speakers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .speaker-card {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    border: 1px solid rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.3);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .speaker-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.2);
  }

  .speaker-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-green);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .speaker-name {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--text-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .speaker-info {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .video-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .video-card {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .video-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .video-card iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 250px;
  }

  .video-card p {
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-green);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .registration {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: rgba(37, 23, 48, 0.5);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .register-btn-large {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .register-btn-large:hover {
    background: #e55f0a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(253, 115, 24, 0.4);
  }

  .host-info {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .poster {
      max-width: 400px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .event-details p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .speakers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .poster {
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .video-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>